{"tid":806413,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"中學生不應談戀愛","createTime":"2018-09-04T15:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T13:50:19.000Z","uid":178205,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4f4c1eaa887d220c40723fadaa30386b4eb138dc","tid":806413,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"有冇人老豆老母係咁老土，唔俾拍拖<br />\n<br />\n睇住個中學，好鍾意嘅人俾mk溝咗，但係無膽去馬<br />\n<br />\n結果25歲仲係含自己<br />\n<br />\n(中一果陣俾女追一齊咗，老豆知道之後威脅我，<br />\n條女一打嚟(冇手提)就屌到佢飛天)<br />\n果時細路一個唯有分手<br />\n以後都唔敢識女<br />\n<br />\n睇見佢而家七十幾話叫我識女，心諗收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2fcd2c3dbb6bc2adab37e29257cdc4cd57ee8c","tid":806413,"uid":178205,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:10:11.000Z","msg":"我諗得我老豆咁撚柒鳩<br />\n係咪整定天煞孤星"},{"pid":"b820aa21bb97cfc6c0ce85fd38f8bb1993f74fc0","tid":806413,"uid":200682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:20:44.000Z","msg":"搞機激下老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ac02405e8ed86ff6c20f8a938979bc7b49e829","tid":806413,"uid":178205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b820aa21bb97cfc6c0ce85fd38f8bb1993f74fc0","tid":806413,"uid":200682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:20:44.000Z","msg":"搞機激下老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:59:56.000Z","msg":"全港最大基壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9823eedf8dc5819d2d37111a640102267fb7add","tid":806413,"uid":71508,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:21:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中學一定要拍拖！</span>"},{"pid":"7e8c7d55b59add3966f72a1da1f96db212ca8432","tid":806413,"uid":178205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a9823eedf8dc5819d2d37111a640102267fb7a